{"type":null,"faqId":38515,"title":"开启防误触模式","answer":"<meta http-equiv=\"Content-Type\" content=\"text/html; charset=UTF-8\">\n<style type=\"text/css\">.b1{white-space-collapsing:preserve;}\n.d1{margin: 1.18125in 0.7875in 1.18125in 0.7875in;}\n.p1{margin-left:1.18125in;margin-top:0.11111111in;margin-bottom:0.11111111in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Arial;font-size:10pt;}\n.p2{margin-left:1.18125in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Arial;font-size:10pt;}\n.p3{text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Arial;font-size:10pt;}\n.p4{margin-top:0.055555556in;margin-bottom:0.055555556in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Arial;font-size:10pt;}\n.td1{width:0.82708335in;padding-start:0.075in;padding-end:0.075in;border-bottom:thin solid black;border-left:thin solid black;border-right:thin solid black;border-top:thin solid black;}\n.td2{width:4.6854167in;padding-start:0.075in;padding-end:0.075in;border-bottom:thin solid black;border-left:thin solid black;border-right:thin solid black;border-top:thin solid black;}\n.r1{keep-together:always;}\n.t1{table-layout:fixed;border-collapse:collapse;border-spacing:0;}\n</style>\n<div>\n<p>\n<span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\"><span>开启防误触模式，可防止手机在口袋中由于挤压或滑动引起的误操作。</span>\n</span></p>\n<p>\n<span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\"><span>在主屏幕，点击“</span><img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=125550\" style=\"width:0.25555557in;height:0.18680556in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"><span>”“设置”，然后切换到“全部设置”页签。</span>\n</span></p>\n<p>\n<span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\"><span>在“智能辅助”区域，点击“更多”。</span>\n</span></p>\n<p>\n<span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\"><span>点击“防误触模式”开关，开启防误触模式。在防误触模式下，当屏幕顶端被遮挡时，点亮屏幕后的滑屏操作将失效。取消遮挡后，屏幕操作即可恢复至正常状态。</span>\n</span></p>\n<p></p>\n<p></p>\n<p>\n<span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\"><span>1.</span><a name=\"_topic_app_center001-chtext\"><span> </span><span>应用市场</span></a>\n</span></p>\n<p>\n<span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\"><span>在主屏幕，点击“</span><img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=125551\" style=\"width:0.25555557in;height:0.18680556in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"><span>”“应用市场”。</span>\n</span></p>\n<p>\n<span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\"><img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=125552\" style=\"width:3.0in;height:3.0in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"></span></p>\n<p></p>\n<table class=\"t1\">\n  <tbody>\n    <tr class=\"r1\">\n      <td class=\"td1\">\n      <p class=\"p4\">\n      <span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\"><img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=125553\" style=\"width:0.22569445in;height:0.16597222in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"></span></p>\n      </td>\n      <td class=\"td2\">\n      <p class=\"p4\">\n      <span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\"><span>安装二维码扫描识别工具。</span>\n      </span></p>\n      </td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr class=\"r1\">\n      <td class=\"td1\">\n      <p class=\"p4\">\n      <span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\"><img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=125554\" style=\"width:0.22569445in;height:0.16597222in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"></span></p>\n      </td>\n      <td class=\"td2\">\n      <p class=\"p4\">\n      <span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\"><span>管理应用程序和安装包，进行应用体检、应用搬家和零流量传输等操作。</span>\n      </span></p>\n      </td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr class=\"r1\">\n      <td class=\"td1\">\n      <p class=\"p4\">\n      <span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\"><img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=125555\" style=\"width:0.22569445in;height:0.16597222in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"></span></p>\n      </td>\n      <td class=\"td2\">\n      <p class=\"p4\">\n      <span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\"><span>管理帐号、设置更新包下载方式、开启消息提示和清空缓存等。</span>\n      </span></p>\n      </td>\n    </tr>\n  </tbody>\n</table>\n<p></p